<div class="visitor_chat" style="position: relative;">
  <div class="after-chat-information" id="after-chat-information-02">
    <img src="<%= asset_path("growth_challenge_logo.png") %>" style="margin: auto;
            display: block;
            width: 270px;
            padding-bottom: 16px;">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-9 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <p>You are here because a friend of yours, <strong>{{friendsName || friendsEmail}}</strong>, thought you would be able to talk with them and help
          them grow closer to Jesus Christ.<br>
          A spiritual mentor is like a coach. In Matthew 28, Jesus tells us to "go and make disciples." This simply
          means helping others learn to follow Jesus. This is a chance for you to do that with someone you already know!
        </p>

        <p>To accept this challenge, enter your email below</p>
        <ul>
          <li>We won't share your information with anyone. Only you and your friend will receive a confirmation
            message.
          </li>
          <li>We will email you four thought-provoking videos with discussion questions and mentoring tips that will
            assist you in helping your friend understand something very important about their relationship with God. You
            can get a preview of the emails <a href="/challenge/resources" target="_blank">here</a>.
          </li>
          <li>This will also let us know that you will be connecting with your friend and helping them take the next
            step to grow toward Jesus.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p style="padding-top:20px;"><strong>Join the challenge</strong>:</p>

        <div style="margin:20px auto 0 auto;width:85%;display:block;height:140px;" data-ng-show="successfulSubscribe==''">
          <input type="email" class="form-control" ng-enter="emailSubscribe()" placeholder="Email Address..." data-ng-model="visitor_email">

          <div class='btn btn-success btn-block' data-ng-click="emailSubscribe()">Continue ></div>
        </div>

        <div data-ng-show="successfulSubscribe != ''"><p>{{successfulSubscribe}}</p></div>
        <br>

        <p style="font-size: 60%;">*<a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#privacy-policy">Privacy policy</a> -
          We won't sell or torture your personal data :)</p>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <iframe style="margin:auto; display:block; max-width: 100%;" width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/KGlx11BxF24?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <p>Watch #FallingPlates, the 4 minute video above, to see what started the conversation between you and your friend.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<privacy-policy></privacy-policy>